 v5.6X software series was released in FY 2021 and continues to be delivered adding additional capabilities across the Fleet FRUs (135 Total: 85 Surface and 50 Subsurface), labs, and training classrooms. The
 TTWCS v7.X software suite began development in 2024. Funds continue to support TTWCS viability and ensure compliance with cybersecurity mandates, and address hardware obsolescence through periodic$$, NULL, $$Exhibit P-40, Budget Line Item Justification: PB 2027 Navy                                                                                                                     Date: April 2026
