 Standardization compatibility. This family of containers includes the Palletized Container (PALCON), Quadruple Container (QUADCON), and Quadruple Container with Roll-up door (QUADCON RUD).

 Corrosion Prevention and Control (CPAC) Program extends Marine Corps tactical equipment life through comprehensive corrosion management. Supporting Force Modernization readiness, CPAC oversees
 preventive and corrective corrosion control for systems including JLTV, ULTV, ACV, MTVR, and LVSR. The program provides total lifecycle solutions focused on cost reduction and improved readiness in
 saltwater and corrosive environments through corrosion prevention compounds and materials, enhancing Marine Corps operations in the Indo-Pacific under EABO and LOCE doctrines.


